  <CalDefinition Description="All amplifier outputs including both the CSM and Low Radio’s internal amplifiers as well as those in a remote amplifier shall provide some form of Dynamic Distortion Limiting to minimize or eliminate clipping of the amplifier speaker output and minimize speaker distortions" Name="FrontRearLimiterCombination" References="GIS-604-240 Dynamic Distortion Limiting (DDL)" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
